{"tid":1616382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"健乜仔姐 個個懶熟咁","createTime":"2019-10-03T11:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T20:08:06.000Z","uid":91454,"like":35,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d443d29d293705f2342083ce76b0393d935163f","tid":1616382,"uid":91454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"應該叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">健英雄</span></span>啊<br />\n或者叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曾英雄</span></span><br />\n雖然大家都唔想呢件事發生<br />\n亦最好唔好發生<br />\n但曾英雄的確係捨身為我地製造左一粒大核彈<br />\n甚至影響到英國班和理非都出聲遣責<br />\n令世界再一次緊緊關注香港發生緊既事<br />\n呢種無私既精神值得我地每個人尊重<br />\n我地應該要高度讚揚呢種精神<br />\n佢係民族英雄<br />\n要受世人標榜同尊重<br />\n從今日開始<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正其名為曾英雄！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7c00c9be5fb64653093e56e6eca37420e5b4d9d2","tid":1616382,"uid":303450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c42f54ba2dd248f3e719acdaef8fbb343ffb95","tid":1616382,"uid":91454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"c934218766ebd89f9406af650cf00d03fdd2fb64","tid":1616382,"uid":91454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49669c4724c4a3626fd43624a07676903a8a7434","tid":1616382,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"曾少俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9150a3e3d3a5b486d0067716100